name: environmental-risk
notes: The Identified Sites coverage, used to support the environmental quality program, references types and concentrations of contaminants, contaminated media and responsible parties across the state. The Treatment Storage and Disposal Site coverage, used to support the environmental quality programs, references hazardous waste generation sites and storage methods. The coverage data is current as of publication date. The KDHE operational databases are dynamic databases.
